text.tspan: 1 ## Showcasing diagnostic comments. Available via code-actions and quickfixes
10 ## By default, a document assumes all globally allowed diagnostics should be shown.
11 ## To disable all diagnostics for a document, place `# @fish-lsp-disable` on line 1.
13 ## Diagnostic comments can include diagnostic code(s)
# disabled alias usage & non-escaped expansion variables
18 ## Diagnostic comments can control ranges of lines
'ALL diagnostics will be DISABLED till EOF unless otherwise enabled'
# 4004 not shown because @fish-lsp-disable is disabling till EOF
33 ## Warn the user of any unknown diagnostic code(s).
■ Invalid diagnostic code: '50010'. Valid codes are: 10
